divs: sighting detailswhile out shopping in the lawrenceville\princeton, nj area on july 10, 2012, around 3pm, i was observing the beautiful clouds in the sky. i felt i had to take a photo of them. i snapped two photos with my cell phone camera: one at 3:04pm and another at 3:06pm both facing north. after downloading the photos to my computer, i noticed a strangely-shaped, dark object in front of one of the puffy white clouds on the first photo. the object is not on the second photo. i did not notice the object in the sky at the time, so i didn't observe any movement or sound. the camera screen was hard to see in the bright sunlight; i just aimed and snapped. it was a busy parking lot with lots of car and people activity. i have no idea what the object was.
Summary: Object was noticed only after downloading photo from cell phone to computer.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Princeton
